                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d571">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 125.36582/123</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Special
                        Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 12, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You will travel with Villa until we can find someone to take your place, a
                    difficult task, owing to the limited number of persons possessing the requisite
                    qualifications, namely, loyalty to the administration, having the friendship of
                    Villa and a knowledge of the Spanish language. Keep us fully informed as to
                    progress of events.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
